Below is the representation of the architecture for the sample project. 



+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                           Terraform                           |
|                                                              |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
| |  Variables  | -> | Configuration | -> | Infrastructure |   |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
|                                                              |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
                                  |
                                  |
                                  v
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                            Jenkins                           |
|                                                              |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
| |   Checkout  | -> | Terraform Init| -> | Terraform Plan |   |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
|                                 |                            |
|                                 v                            |
| +-------------+    +---------------+                         |
| | Terraform   | <- | Terraform Apply|                         |
| | Artifacts   |    +---------------+                         |
| +-------------+                                             |
|                                                              |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
                                  |
                                  |
                                  v
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        AWS CodePipeline                      |
|                                                              |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
| |   Source    | -> |   Buildspec   | -> |   Deployment  |   |
| | (CodeCommit)|    |  (CodeBuild)  |    | (CloudFormation)|   |
| +-------------+    +---------------+    +---------------+   |
|                                 |                            |
|                                 v                            |
| +-------------+    +---------------+                         |
| | Pipeline    | <- | Terraform Artifacts                     |
| | Artifacts   |    +---------------+                         |
| +-------------+                                             |
|                                                              |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
